  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The present study was designed to compare the efficacy of conservative treatment to operative
      treatment for improvement of constipation symptoms in children with Hirschsprung allied
      disease
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The present study was designed to compare the efficacy of conservative treatment,such as anal
      dilatation, colonic lavage and so on, to operative treatment for improvement of constipation
      symptoms in children with Hirschsprung allied disease
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
